# 🍏 Apple Clone Website

This is a responsive Apple website clone built entirely using HTML and CSS. 
-It s a front-end practice project that replicates the look and feel of the official Apple homepage
images/Screenshot 2025-04-21 220128.png


![alt text](<images/Screenshot 2025-04-21 220128.png>)


## 🚀 Features

- 📱 Fully responsive design
- ✨ Smooth transitions and hover effects
- 🧱 Pixel-perfect layout inspired by Apple’s clean design
- 🌐 Semantic HTML structure and modern CSS techniques

## 🛠️ Built With

- HTML5
- CSS3
- Flexbox & Grid Layout





## 📌 Note

This project is purely for educational and portfolio purposes. All design elements are inspired by [apple.com](https://www.apple.com).


